## Development

### Setup

- Install `hatch`
- Create hatch environment

```
hatch env create
```

### Execute Tests

```
hatch run pytest
```

### Build

```
hatch build
```

### Release

- Increase version, then

```
hatch build
hatch publish -u __token__ -a <PyPiToken>
```

